.item
  .label.label-success Happy 20th Birthday Sympa!
  .date 2017-03-21
  .text
    Sympa, the software that makes 20k lists at [[https://lists.riseup.net]]  possible, is turning 20 years old! There will be a hackathon on April 1,2 to celebrate, see [[https://www.sympa.org]] for more details.
.item
  .label.label-warning Updates to legacy VPN
  .date 2017-03-02
  .text
    Attention VPN Red users: we just updated to modern crypto settings which will require client configuration changes. Please review the [[updated help pages->vpn-red]], and adjust your settings. Bitmask (aka "VPN Black") users are unaffected.
.item
  .label.label-danger We have moved to encrypted email storage!
  .date 2017-02-16
  .text
    Starting today, as a response to recent [[legal requests->about-us/press/canary-statement]], all new Riseup email accounts will feature personally encrypted storage on our servers, only accessible by you. In the near future, we will begin to migrate all existing accounts to use this new system.
.item
  .label.label-warning help us stabilize!
  .date 2016-09-07
  .text
    Due to your amazing support, you bought us time until our yearly fundraiser rolls around. However, if you can setup a regular, monthly contribution, even of $1USD, it would help us immensely! Its tiny, but if enough people do it, it will add up, and maybe we can get rid of these annoying requests for money all the time.
.item
  .label.label-danger riseup needs help!
  .date 2016-09-06
  .text
    We are in a financial crisis and need your support! That's why we launched our $1 campaign, where we're asking every riseup user to give us just $1 a month! You can help [[here-->/donate]].
.item
  .label.label-warning Mail may be rejected if you do not use our SMTP server!
  .date 2016-04-04
  .text
    When you send mail from your riseup email account, you need to make sure you are sending it [[through the riseup SMTP server->/email/settings/smtp#how-do-i-configure-smtp]], or they will possibly be rejected by the remote server.

